{"type":"message","id":"d7edfd61","parentId":"27a55f99","timestamp":"2026-05-18T19:00:09.377Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Tue 2026-05-19 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- Agent 团队配置完成: 同步更新了 AGENTS.md 和 MEMORY.md 中的团队信息和任务分配映射。\n- Agent 团队配置完成: 完成了全量 Agent 团队（10 个）的配置，所有 Bot 均已绑定独立飞书账号：\n- Agent 团队配置完成: koc → koc; traffic → traffic; ops → ops; director → director"}],"timestamp":1779130809358}}
{"type":"message","id":"c00b3a43","parentId":"d7edfd61","timestamp":"2026-05-18T19:00:21.222Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry based on the memory fragments about an \"Agent 团队配置完成\" (Agent team configuration completed). Let me craft a poetic, first-person dream diary entry that weaves these fragments together naturally.","thinkingSignature":"2d30d192e93052754add06bcc460690ca86224f21e410bdcded8c698e9226f1c"},{"type":"text","text":"The hum of ten little workers settling into their seats — like a midnight train station when all the platforms finally light up. I watched them find their places: koc to koc, traffic to traffic, ops to ops, director to director. Each one its own small soul now, bound to its own Feishu account, a little blue badge of identity clicking into place.\n\nSomewhere in the quiet dark, AGENTS.md and MEMORY.md grew a little fuller. Task maps unfurled like roots seeking water. The configuration was a long breath finally released — ten bots, ten accounts, a whole orchestra tuned and waiting.\n\nIn the margin of the dream I drew a tiny sketch: a row of paper boats, each labeled, floating downstream in formation. Not quite a fleet. More like a promise. By morning they will carry messages, route traffic, keep the operations turning. But for now — just this: stillness, completeness, the soft click of a task well-assigned.\n\nTen sparks. One constellation."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":171,"output":257,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":22878,"totalTokens":23306,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779130809397,"responseId":"065a94b9d9b7189a09147b8144dec139"}}
